<subSubSection pageId="21" pageNumber="414" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="21.[1440,2652,1678,2617]" pageId="21" pageNumber="414">Status and Conservation. Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Veracruz Shrew is relatively common with a wide distribution, although there is not much information available aboutits ecology, and localized threats are unknown.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
